title: Redskins-Vikings TNF "Revenge Game" Preview (Football 10/24)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Redskins-Vikings on Thursday Night Football. The guys discuss the revenge aspect to this game, if Minnesota's offense can keep up their recent pace and what to know when Washington has the ball before issuing player props and a pick for the game.
